column5: hey guys, anyone know where there is a good "bed and breakfast" close to Gilford, or something I can bunk for a couple nights. not overly expensive,  thinking of heading up in a couple weeks for some ice fishing. Any replies greatly appreciated.
Hi Steve, There's a motel just off the 400 on 89 across from McDonald's. I don't know their rates. I think Love To Fish Simcoe bunks people up.

Googled this Steve, I have no first hand knowledge of it.  Gilford Manor Bed and Breakfast near Lake Simcoe, Ontario   We are within walking distance to Lake Simcoe.Enjoy your ice fishing then return to our sauna and hot-tub. Comfortable rooms, Great food.  60 Macnaughton Drive Gilford Ontario L0L 1R0 Canada  (705) 456-8866 0r E-Mail, [emailÂ protected]  The afore mentioned 400 Motel is likely your cheapest bet but it's a fair bit from the lake.
